The '''Lion Circus''' is a building in the [[Elite Barracks]] category. It is used to spawn [[Griffin]]s.

== Production ==
The Lion Circus produces one [[Griffin]] every 10 seconds. It consumes 20 [[Meat]] and 20 [[Wheat]] per cycle.

